        filter_upwards [h]
        intro a h‚ÇÅa h‚ÇÇa
        have h‚ÇÉa : ‚àÄ·∂† (y : ‚ÑÇ) in ùìù a, y ‚â† z := by
          exact ContinuousAt.eventually_ne (fun ‚¶ÉU‚¶Ñ a ‚Ü¶ a) h‚ÇÇa
        filter_upwards [h‚ÇÅa h‚ÇÇa, h‚ÇÉa]
